data.text:
Shipping is fast & free on most orders shipped within the United States. Orders will ship via USPS Priority Mail and include tracking confirmation. Expedited shipping is available at extra charge. International delivery rates vary by destination.

Shipping for Mystery Boxes is $15 for Domestic orders. AC at Home & Private Signing shipping costs will vary dependent upon series.

International delivery rates vary by destination. International orders may be subject to Customs charges paid by receiver upon delivery. These charges are subject to individual country regulation. Prime Time Signatures does not control customs charges.

Prime Time Signatures is dedicated in providing 100% authentic autographed memorabilia and collectibles. All autographs are obtained in person by Prime Time Signature’s staff. To verify the authenticity of your purchase, all items can be viewed through their unique certification number on our website, or a third party authentication company. This number can be found on the item’s Certificate of Authenticity, as well as the tamper-proof hologram affixed to the item.
